00:36:52.308 --> 00:36:53.389
Tawagan ang mga guro!

00:36:53.847 --> 00:36:54.974
Bakit kailangan mong gawin ito?

00:36:54.998 --> 00:36:56.103
Paano mo magagawa?

00:36:56.368 --> 00:36:56.985
Atom!

