Ang Board Game Club.

00:40:14.640 --> 00:40:15.770
SAMPUNG PANIG DICE

00:40:15.780 --> 00:40:16.780
ANG SIMBOL SA DICE

00:40:23.893 --> 00:40:24.893
Tingnan mo.

00:40:25.470 --> 00:40:26.950
Katulad talaga ng larong nilaro namin.

00:40:31.349 --> 00:40:33.629
Ibig sabihin, galing talaga
sa Board Game Club ang dice na ito.

00:40:33.779 --> 00:40:36.499
Pero never may club na ganyan ang school namin.

00:40:36.977 --> 00:40:41.002
Kung meron man,
dapat bago pa ako makapasok sa paaralang ito.

00:40:45.917 --> 00:40:47.404
Ang Taon 1995.

00:40:48.207 --> 00:40:50.503
Siguro may club na ito 30 years ago.

00:40:58.503 --> 00:40:59.503
Tingnan mo.

00:41:00.725 --> 00:41:01.725
Sino ang…

00:41:02.280 --> 00:41:03.380
Babala?

00:41:05.623 --> 00:41:07.595
Baka member siya ng club.

00:41:09.296 --> 00:41:10.801
Kung mahahanap natin si Panyada,

00:41:11.281 --> 00:41:12.896
baka marami pa tayong alam tungkol sa dice na ito.

00:41:15.640 --> 00:41:18.050
IMBESTIGATOR

00:41:20.645 --> 00:41:21.645
Dito.

00:41:23.139 --> 00:41:24.840
Ang mga yearbook ng paaralan.

00:41:25.240 --> 00:41:27.250
Mayroong impormasyon tungkol sa
mga mag-aaral sa bawat taon.

00:41:27.794 --> 00:41:31.303
Sa log book,
binanggit ni Panyada ang taon bilang 1995.

00:41:31.782 --> 00:41:37.602
Maaari siyang mag-aaral dito
simula noong 1993, hindi ba?

00:41:40.170 --> 00:41:41.170
Tingnan natin siya.

00:42:08.945 --> 00:42:11.000
Tiningnan namin ang lahat.

00:42:11.472 --> 00:42:14.103
Paanong wala sa sinumang
may pangalang Panyada?

00:42:42.760 --> 00:42:43.850
1996/1994

00:42:47.256 --> 00:42:48.400
What’s wrong, Samut?

00:42:52.730 --> 00:42:54.201
Ang mga yearbook na ito…

00:42:54.429 --> 00:42:55.601
Kulang ang isa.

00:42:57.277 --> 00:42:58.320
Ang 1995 Yearbook.

